column5: hey everyone, I looking at booking a campsite at Mikisew provincial park in a weeks time and I'm trying to find a little info about the fishing. I'm been doing some research but having a tough time as there are a lot of eagle lakes in Ontario and I'm not sure if I'm getting the right info. I will be fishing mostly out a kayak or canoe. I'm assuming it's mostly bass, pike and walleye in there. Does anyone have any experience fishing this Eagle lake they'd be willing to share?  Thanks
No, the lake I'm talking about is close to South River and Sunridge.
